---
// Componente de Proyectos Destacados y Trayectoria
---

<section id="proyectos" class="py-24 px-6 relative">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    {/* Encabezado de Sección */}
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">
        Casos de <span class="text-emerald-500">Éxito</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full mb-4"></div>

      <p class="text-white/50 text-lg max-w-2xl text-left">
        Una selección de soluciones técnicas que han marcado la diferencia,
        desde sistemas de emergencia hasta infraestructuras críticas.
      </p>
    </div>

    {/* Proyecto Destacado: QR SalvaVidas */}
    <div class="mb-20">
      <div
        class="bg-linear-to-br from-blue-600/10 to-emerald-600/10 rounded-[48px] border border-white/5 p-8 md:p-20 relative overflow-hidden group"
      >
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="text-left">
            <div
              class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold mb-6 border border-emerald-500/20 uppercase tracking-[3px]"
            >
              Proyecto Destacado
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-5xl font-black mb-6 leading-none text-white">
              QR SalvaVidas
            </h3>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
              Plataforma crítica diseñada para centralizar información médica
              vital accesible mediante escaneo QR. Un reto de arquitectura
              enfocado en la disponibilidad absoluta y seguridad de datos.
            </p>

            <div class="flex gap-12 mb-10">
              <div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">&lt; 1s</div>
                <div
                  class="text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1"
                >
                  Respuesta
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">100%</div>
                <div
                  class="text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1"
                >
                  Uptime
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-10">
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg text-[10px] font-mono text-white/60"
                >Node.js</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg text-[10px] font-mono text-white/60"
                >PWA</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg text-[10px] font-mono text-white/60"
                >AES-256</span
              >
            </div>

            <a
              href="/proyectos"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-emerald-400 font-bold hover:gap-5 transition-all group"
            >
              Explorar arquitectura <span
                class="material-symbols-rounded transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"
                >arrow_forward</span
              >
            </a>
          </div>

          {/* Visualización del Proyecto */}
          <div class="relative flex justify-center">
            <div
              class="glass-card p-4 rounded-4xl transform rotate-2 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-700 shadow-2xl bg-black/40 border-white/10"
            >
              <div
                class="w-64 aspect-9/16 bg-[#0D1117] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center p-8 border border-white/5 overflow-hidden relative"
              >
                <div
                  class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-emerald-500/10 to-transparent"
                >
                </div>
                <div class="relative z-10 text-center">
                  <div
                    class="w-20 h-20 border-2 border-emerald-500/40 rounded-3xl mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center animate-pulse"
                  >
                    <span
                      class="material-symbols-rounded text-emerald-500 text-5xl font-light"
                      >qr_code_2</span
                    >
                  </div>
                  <div class="h-1.5 w-24 bg-white/20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-3">
                  </div>
                  <div class="h-1.5 w-16 bg-white/10 rounded-full mx-auto">
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            {/* Decoración flotante */}
            <div
              class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 glass-card p-5 rounded-2xl hidden md:block border-blue-500/30"
            >
              <p
                class="text-[9px] font-bold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 text-left"
              >
                Lead Architect
              </p>
              <p class="font-bold text-white text-sm">Jorge Borges</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Otros Proyectos / Trayectoria */}
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {/* Proyecto: Lottery */}
      <div
        class="glass-card p-8 rounded-4xl border-white/5 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all group"
      >
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
          <span
            class="text-[10px] font-bold text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[3px]"
            >1999 — 2000</span
          >
          <span
            class="material-symbols-rounded text-blue-500 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
            >open_in_new</span
          >
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 text-left">
          Lottery 95 / 2000
        </h4>
        <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed text-left mb-6">
          Pionero en sistemas de venta de lotería en Windows con transmisión vía
          módem. Un hito en la digitalización de juegos de azar en Venezuela.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-1 bg-white/5 rounded text-white/60"
            >VB 5.0</span
          >
          <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-1 bg-white/5 rounded text-white/60"
            >Modem Data</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Proyecto: JBConta */}
      <div
        class="glass-card p-8 rounded-4xl border-white/5 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all group"
      >
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
          <span
            class="text-[10px] font-bold text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[3px]"
            >ERP System</span
          >
          <span
            class="material-symbols-rounded text-blue-500 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
            >open_in_new</span
          >
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 text-left">JBConta ERP</h4>
        <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed text-left mb-6">
          Sistema integral de inventarios y facturación masiva. Gestión técnica
          de +16,000 artículos con integración de hardware periférico.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-1 bg-white/5 rounded text-white/60"
            >VB.NET</span
          >
          <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-1 bg-white/5 rounded text-white/60"
            >SQL Server</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Proyecto: TiendaLumi */}
      <div
        class="glass-card p-8 rounded-4xl border-white/5 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all group"
      >
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
          <span
            class="text-[10px] font-bold text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[3px]"
            >E-commerce</span
          >
          <span
            class="material-symbols-rounded text-blue-500 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
            >open_in_new</span
          >
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 text-left">TiendaLumi</h4>
        <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed text-left mb-6">
          Arquitectura robusta para comercio electrónico en Argentina. Enfoque
          en escalabilidad y experiencia de usuario fluida.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-1 bg-white/5 rounded text-white/60"
            >PHP</span
          >
          <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-1 bg-white/5 rounded text-white/60"
            >MySQL</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

